  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/786470/extras/4f5d1dacb93c620a031846d249a48b35.avif?t=1710338083\" width=512 height=540 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >main content: </h2><strong>This is an action role-playing game, you need to play Zhou Xin, secretly assign the resistance army and fight to the enemy , to explore the vast world of Bashu, to unit your forces everywhere, wandering in the geography wastelade, and pick up anything to upgrade your equipment</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features: </h2><strong>Danmaku shooting and platform jumping, you must think about both.</strong><br><strong>You often need to consider your firearms, line of sight, weapons collection and derivation ... </strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >World Settings: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Located in a closed crystalline wall system, resources are not replenished, so the need for special supply mode<br></li><li>Even in the closed world, the sense of struggle of mankind will not disappear, so the formation of a separatist force<br></li><li>The protagonist Zhou Xin, a starlady of 28 Chinese horoscopes (Wei Yue Yan, the dangerous moon-swallow) , the remaining characters are designed according Chinese mythological creatures.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/786470/extras/4f5d1dacb93c620a031846d249a48b35.avif?t=1710338083\" width=512 height=540 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >main content: </h2><strong>This is an action role-playing game, you need to play Zhou Xin, secretly assign the resistance army and fight to the enemy , to explore the vast world of Bashu, to unit your forces everywhere, wandering in the geography wastelade, and pick up anything to upgrade your equipment</strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features: </h2><strong>Danmaku shooting and platform jumping, you must think about both.</strong><br><strong>You often need to consider your firearms, line of sight, weapons collection and derivation ... </strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >World Settings: </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Located in a closed crystalline wall system, resources are not replenished, so the need for special supply mode<br></li><li>Even in the closed world, the sense of struggle of mankind will not disappear, so the formation of a separatist force<br></li><li>The protagonist Zhou Xin, a starlady of 28 Chinese horoscopes (Wei Yue Yan, the dangerous moon-swallow) , the remaining characters are designed according Chinese mythological creatures.</li></ul>",
